<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>WorkIQ Password Reset Email</title>
    <style type="text/css">
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            min-width: 100%;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            background-color: #f4f7f6;
            color: #333333;
        }
        a { 
            color: #0070f3;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        h1 {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 700;
            line-height: 1.3;
            margin-top: 0;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            color: #e3eeff;
        }
      span {
        color: #0070f3;
      }
        p {
            margin-top: 0;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #555555;
        }
        .email-wrapper {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            background-color: #ffffff;
        }
        .email-header {
            background-color: #0070f3;
            padding: 24px;
            color: #ffffff;
            border-top-left-radius: 8px;
            border-top-right-radius: 8px;
        }
        .email-body {
            padding: 24px;
        }
        .email-footer {
            background-color: #f6f6f6;
            padding: 24px;
            border-bottom-left-radius: 8px;
            border-bottom-right-radius: 8px;
        }
        .activation-code {
            background: #00466a;
            color: #ffffff;
            margin: 0 auto;
          padding: 8px;
						width: max-content;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #0070f3;
            color: #ffffff;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 700;
            text-align: center;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-wrapper">
        <div class="email-header">
            <h1>WorkIQ</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="email-body">
          <p style="font-size: 20px;">Hello <span> <%= user.name %> </span> ,</p>
            <p>You recently requested to reset the password for your WorkIQ account.</p>
            <p>Please use the following code:</p>
            <div class="activation-code"><%= activationCode %></div>
            <p style="font-size: 18px;">Please enter this code on the activation page within the next 5 minutes.</p>
            <p>If you did not request a password reset, please ignore this email or reply to let us know.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="email-footer">
            <p>If you have any questions, please don't hesitate to contact us at <a href="mailto:musamuhammedolayinka@gmail.com">WorkIQ</a>.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
